r of dots between lettersBR                     control breakDA 0-3               0 darkness control, std printDA on,off          off Darkness (vertical), graphics fontsEM on,off          off Emphasized print, graphics fontsCB n,w                 multiple columns: #, widthCB -n,w                columns separated by vertical linesPR on,off          off Proportional print, graphics fontsKR on,off          off Kerning print,graphics fontsKS n                 0 Kerning Space, vertical separationSW n                 5 Space Width INDENTATION----------- IN 0, n, -n         0  left margin indentation in 1/10"OF n                   delayed indent, manually controlledPP in                  new paragraph: indentCE ON, OFF, W     off  centering  SPACING-------SK n, -n               skip 'n' lines forward, 'n' lines backPA                     start new pageCP n                   conditional new pageCC n                   conditional new columnLH n               12  Line Height in dotsDS on,off         off  Double SpaceVT                     Vertical tab, record current positionVT n                   Vertical tab, n lines from page topFILES-----IM fid                 imbed another fileAP fid                 append another fileTC string              table of contents entryIX string              index entryRD sym,fid             form letter reads from N&A fileKE "message"           keyboard entry of text or command  FONTS------ BF fileid            1  Begin Font "fileid" or 1 for std fontAF fileid               Alternate Font "fileid"AF fileid-n             Alternate Font lowered n lines                           (subscript)TF fileid            1  Title Font "fileid"MF n                 1  Magnify font by factor of nRE 0,1,2             0  Reverse: no, non-blank, all  TITLES------ TT text                top titleBT text                bottom titleTF fileid              Title Font "fileid"PN ON,OFF          on  page numberingPS c                $  page number symbol used in titles  MISCELLANEOUS------------- CW char             .  control word character (usually . or ;)ES char             !  escape sequence character (@ or !)CM anything            comment, rest of line ignoredSY @nnn,nnn,nnn        ASCII symbols to go as-is to printerTR a,b,c               character translationHY c,ON,OFF            hyphenation controlsPG s,n                 page range to be printedST message             stop for operator interventionEN                     END of document. Must be lastIG on,off,1,2     off  IGnore ON= ignore until IG OFF                         1=ignore text, but not dot commands                         2=ignore BF,AF and TF commandsHL                     draw Horizontal Line using current                          UP settingUP n                1  Underline Pin settingVL on,off,1,2,3   off  Vertical Line: ON or 1 in left margin                          2=Vertical Line in both margins                          3=Vertical Line in right margin ESCAPE SEQUENCES---------------- !$                     start underlining, blank & non-blank!&                     start underlining non-blanks!%                     end   underlining!(                     start double width!)                     end   double width!/                     start alternate character set!?                     end   alternate character set  MINI-EDIT---------hold <SHIFT> until program asks for keyboard entry.       Then enter commands or line of text